name: Sarah Johnson
message: We're looking for a manufacturing partner for our new product line. Need someone with aerospace certifications and high-volume capabilities. Would like to schedule a facility tour.

name: Michael Chen
message: Interested in your automotive manufacturing capabilities. We have a potential contract for suspension components that would require IATF 16949 certification. Please contact me to discuss volumes and pricing.

name: Jennifer Lee
message: We need a manufacturing partner for FDA-regulated medical device components. Quality and traceability are critical. Do you have experience with medical device manufacturing and FDA compliance?
